data.description: This is a classic chalet cabin.  It has been completely renovated with: new insulation new sheetrock, new doors, new windows, new roof, new floors, updated bathrooms, new hot water heater, new deck, new kitchen (with all appliances included), a new Bosch compact washer/dryer unit, new wood stove, and new paint inside/out.
data.whatILove: This home is on a large naturally landscaped lot in a gated community (Lake Holiday) and is close to a playground with tennis courts, softball field and a children's play area.  The house is set back from the road for maximum privacy and has a very nice back yard area.  It has an office with a balcony overlooking the front yard and 3 other bedrooms.  The living area is an open concept kitchen, living room area.  It's a small but very cozy place.
